# Keep the build context lean: without this, COPY backend/ and COPY frontend/
# dragged in ~200 MB of macOS-native venv/node_modules that either bloated the
# arm64 image or overlaid the builder's own npm ci output.
**/node_modules
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
backend/.venv
backend/test_*.py
frontend/dist
data
*.db
.git
.gitignore
docs
.superpowers
scripts
*.md
.dockerignore
